properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 20 at 1:31PM PST until January 21 at 7:00AM PST by NWS Medford OR
properties.description:
* WHAT...South winds 25 to 30 mph with gusts up to 45 mph
expected.

* WHERE...Southern Rogue Valley to include Ashland, Talent, and
Phoenix as well as hills surrounding the Rogue Valley.

* WHEN...From 8 PM this evening to 7 AM PST Tuesday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds could cause travel difficulties for high
profile vehicles and could blow around unsecured objects.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...

* View the hazard area in detail at
https://www.wrh.noaa.gov/mfr/HAZARD
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 8 PM THIS EVENING TO 7 AM PST TUESDAY
